						               													<description>Build your garden and collect your favorite flower Set to win the game. Gain resources and income to bloom and do evil scheme to sabotage your neighbors.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flower Garden is a gardening game for 2-4 players ages 12+. It is a light-mid weight game and can last for 30 -60 min.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In order to win the game you need to collect 4 of the same color of flowers in your own garden. However there are exactly 4 cards of the same color in the flower deck (Total of 20 flower cards with 5 different color set). In order to collect the flower you need, you would have to sabotage, steal, or change color of your flower.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Before owning flowers, you have to go through the process of gaining seeds and blooming them with resources.&amp;#10;You may sell the flowers to gain income for plan cards. Plan cards will help your garden and/or destroy your neighbors.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To add a twist in the game, there is a Queen card that has 2 different personalities: Flower Queen and Weed Queen. One card with 2 sides. Flower Queen is definitely the queen you need in your garden, you would not want to have Weed Queen destroying your garden. To summon the queen in a garden, a player prays for the queen by scarifying a flower or pay the coins. If another player prays for the queen, she will be moving around different garden depending on the prayer choice.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends as soon as the first player successfully collected 4 colors of the same flower.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
